    <Entry>
      <ID>1</ID>
      <DefaultText>The year is 431 and [url=glossary:kyros]Kyros[/url] invasion has shattered all major opposition in the Tiers.The [url=glossary:younger realms]Younger Realms[/url] the Bastard Tier the Free Cities - all who defied [url=glossary:kyros]Kyros[/url] lay broken by battle or bowed in surrender.

The two armies of the Overlord - the [url=glossary:disfavored]Disfavored[/url] and the [url=glossary:scarlet chorus]Scarlet Chorus[/url] - now control our lands.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>2</ID>
      <DefaultText>Mas a nossa vontade ainda não está extinta, não inteiramente. In the valley of [url=glossary:vendriens well]Vendriens Well[/url] those of us unwilling to bow to [url=glossary:kyros]Kyros[/url] have banded together in defiance.

Violating an oath of surrender from two years prior we have staged a bloody uprising - murdering the [url=glossary:disfavored]Disfavored[/url] and [url=glossary:scarlet chorus]Scarlet Chorus[/url] garrison in a midnight assault.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>5</ID>
      <DefaultText>With their main forces spread across the Tiers the [url=glossary:disfavored]Disfavored[/url] and [url=glossary:scarlet chorus]Scarlet Chorus[/url] redeploy to [url=glossary:vendriens well]Vendriens Well[/url] para esmagar a resistência, mas os meses passam sem batalha definitiva.

Quando o desacordo e a discórdia paralisam os Arcontes, esperamos que a nossa mensagem de insurreição se espalhe pelas camadas.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>6</ID>
      <DefaultText>The Overlord is not amused and [url=glossary:kyros]Kyros[/url] has one message for the Archons: crush the oathbreakers or die.[url=glossary:kyros]Kyros[/url] backs this threat with an [url=glossary:edict]Edict[/url] a magical commandment that can slay all in the valley should the order be ignored.

The honor of proclaiming this [url=glossary:edict]Edict[/url] fell to you.Sent across the mountains to [url=glossary:vendriens well]Vendriens Well[/url] you carry the Overlords [url=glossary:edict]Edict[/url] to read before the Archons.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
